    {
      "number": 3,
      "title": "副词「就」— The Adverb jiù",
      "explanation": "就(jiù) is a versatile adverb with several meanings. 立刻 Right away / immediately: 我就去 (I'll go right away) — use 就 to mean \"right now\". Only / simply / just: 就这样 (just like this) — use 就 to mean \"just\" or \"only\". 条件 Condition-result (with 如果/要是): 如果你来，我就高兴 (If you come, I'll be happy). Directions: 就在那里 (it's right there) — use 就 to mean \"right here/there\".",
